title.narrative: Intensifying targeted HIV Prevention, Care and Treatment Strategies towards achieving the three 90’s targets

description.narrative: Ethiopia - HIV - HIV/AIDS Prevention and Control Office - HAPCO. This program has the following goals: To prevent 70,000 - 80,000 new HIV infections by 2020. Ending TB epidemic in Ethiopia. To save 500,000 - 550,000 lives due to HIV/AIDS by 2020. The objectives of this program are: Improve access to TB,TB/HIV and MDR-TB services. Improve community ownership on TB prevention and control. Implement high impact and targeted prevention programs. Attain Virtual elimination of MTCT of HIV. Intensify targeted HIV testing and counseling. Optimize and sustain high quality care and treatment. Improve quality of TB, TB/HIV and MDR-TB service delivery
